---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

// Newsletter page pointing visitors to your Beehiiv subscription page.  Replace
// the newsletterLink constant with your actual Beehiiv subdomain URL.

// The Beehiiv subscription form is embedded below.  The script and iframe
// provided by Beehiiv are included directly in the page to allow visitors
// to subscribe without leaving the site.

---
<Layout>
  <section class="newsletter">
    <h1>Newsletter</h1>
    <!-- Embed Beehiiv subscribe form directly on the newsletter page -->
    <div class="newsletter-embed">
      <script async src="https://subscribe-forms.beehiiv.com/embed.js"></script>
      <iframe
        src="https://subscribe-forms.beehiiv.com/261a3276-40ab-431a-8523-c85bec095b96"
        class="beehiiv-embed"
        data-test-id="beehiiv-embed"
        frameborder="0"
        scrolling="no"
        style="width: 100%; height: 439px; margin: 0; border-radius: 0; background-color: transparent; box-shadow: 0 0; max-width: 100%;"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  <p>
### Why Subscribe to *Modern Compass*?  
Most personal growth content is noise made up of quick tips and recycled advice. *Modern Compass* is different.  

Each issue gives you:  
- **Clarity without fluff.** Big ideas distilled into practical takeaways.  
- **Proven frameworks.** Tools like *TimeOS* and the *Intention vs. Action* activity to guide real decisions.  
- **Action over theory.** Exercises and reflections you can apply immediately.  
- **Relatable depth.** Stories and examples that stick, not abstract jargon.  

Subscribers also get early access to tools, digital downloads, and updates on the *Modern Compass* book.  

This is not about chasing endless self-improvement. It is about building the compass that helps you navigate life with purpose, trust, and clarity.  

**Join today and start building your Modern Compass.**
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .newsletter {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .newsletter h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .newsletter p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .subscribe-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
    max-width: fit-content;
  }

  .subscribe-button:hover {
    background: var(--accent-color);
  }

  /* Container for the Beehiiv subscription form on the newsletter page */
  .newsletter-embed {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
</style>
